          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Major Medical Facility Authorization Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs to carry out specified major medical facility projects during FY2021. The bill also indicates the maximum amount that can be spent on each project.</p>]]>
